WEBVTT

00:12.950 --> 00:14.150
One silk handkerchief,...

00:16.700 --> 00:17.350
...one watch,...

00:22.400 --> 00:22.950
...one ring,...

00:27.600 --> 00:29.500
...one gold money clip with no money in it,...

00:32.550 --> 00:34.950
...and one mobile phone.

00:52.750 --> 00:56.550
Someone reminded me I once said, "Greed is good".

00:58.700 --> 00:59.900
Now, it seems it's legal.

01:02.500 --> 01:04.000
No matter how much money you make,...

01:04.100 --> 01:04.800
You should get going.

01:05.400 --> 01:06.350
...you'll never be rich.

01:10.800 --> 01:12.600
Why don't you start calling me Gordon?

